Business Brief -- Electrosource Inc.:
   Preferred Stake Sold, Giving
   Ex-Official Voting Control
Electrosource, which does research on batteries, had said
the sale was necessary to restart its operations, which were
suspended in September after a General Motors Corp.
subsidiary stopped supporting its efforts to develop an
experimental battery for electric cars. The preferred stock
sale was announced last month after efforts to merge with a
private company failed.